      <h2 class="section-headline">Stripe won't tell you when your account is at risk.</h2>
      <p class="section-body max-w-lg">
        DTC brands live and die by Stripe. One bad month of chargebacks and your account gets restricted — without warning, without explanation, and with no recourse. By the time you find out, you've already lost access to your revenue.
      </p>
